{
  "texts": [
    "We focus on the G3 subset because it is the most challenging subset in ToolBench.",
    "It requires the combined use of multiple tools from different categories, which helps to reflect complex realworld scenarios.",
    "In addition, ToolBench provides 5,000 instruction-solution pairs for the G3 subset, which are used to train ToolLlama.",
    "These solutions were collected by ChatGPT and employ a reasoning strategy based on Depth First Search-based Decision Tree.",
    "Table 10 shows an instruction example that requires obtaining \"music trivia question\" and \"random trivia question\"."
  ]
}